summary:
While working as a sales representative, a trainer and an export administrative assistant I gained a wide range of skills. Providing services that help companies identify, approach and profit from international market opportunities, enabled me to demonstrate my communication skills, abilities in the commercial, marketing and organization areas. 
As an experienced trainer of Russian language I enjoy working in professional training & coaching industry. Confident teaching one-to-one and in groups. Completely bilingual in Russian and Dutch.
